		<div class="info">
			<h1>April 24, 2014 - George Saunders</h1>
			<div class="meta">
				<ul>
					<li>Episode: 10094</li><li class="need-count"> (0)</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<p>The Supreme Court upholds a ban on affirmative action, a cattle rancher battles the federal government, and author George Saunders discusses "Congratulations, by the way."</p>
			
		</div>
	</div>
   <div class="transcript">
              <div class="act">
